# Sprint 60: Unfixed Problems & New Bugs
# S60.ptl

v:4
role: planner
gate: OPEN

objective: |
  Critical: iOS PWA loader safe area; Object Details scroll (fixed top, list only);
  History Events tabs and back button; header buttons no background; Object list
  date/time formatting; Tracking player API and analytics. Object Details tabs
  and header content; default behavior and map init; History list events and
  Events tab; History page scroll and drag-expand map. Reports table (fixed Vehicle
  column, green total); Tracking no-data toast and footer visibility; Tracking
  Player controls and map interaction. Object list 3-line structure. Login spacing;
  dropdown alignment; icon system; toast system. Global API error handling and
  vehicle cache; report API and Settings; comprehensive API review. Refactoring
  after implementation (structure, duplication, performance). Testing.

requires: [FRONTEND_DEV]
invariants: sprints/54/INVARIANTS.md
design-ref: sprints/56/artifacts/S56-Consolidated-Roadmap.md

###############################################################################
# CONTEXT
###############################################################################
epic: E-05-PWA-UI-IMPLEMENTATION
priority: P0
source: Unfixed Problems & New Bugs Sprint Prompt
target: navitrack-apps (paths.code per project.config.yml)

